## üî¨ Core Innovation: Nano-Channel Platform

{{< figure src="/images/research/integration-concept.png" alt="Research Integration Concept" caption="Bridging cellular reality with molecular precision through nanofluidic confinement" >}}

### The Technical Breakthrough

Our platform uniquely combines three critical elements:

1. **Graduated Nanofluidic Channels (50 nm - 2 ¬µm)**
   - Systematically control spatial confinement
   - Mimic nuclear compartmentalization
   
2. **Multi-Reservoir Microfluidics**
   - Precisely tune molecular crowding (0-300 mg/mL)
   - Real-time buffer exchange
   - Multi-protein competition assays

3. **Single-Molecule Fluorescence (TIRF)**
   - Three-color simultaneous imaging
   - Real-time binding dynamics
   - Sub-second temporal resolution

**Key Advantage:** First platform to independently control AND systematically vary both spatial confinement and molecular crowding.

